Title: Remote BI Aggregations can now be configured to be checked as single services
Level: 1
Component: wato
Compatible: compat
Version: 1.2.5i6
Date: 1413382852
Class: feature

It is now possible to create services out of the total state of local BI aggregations
or BI aggregations of other sites. This can be configured via WATO
(Host & Service Parameters > Active Checks > Check State of BI Aggregation).
